-------------------------------
 NEWS for R Package "VegX"
-------------------------------

__Version history__

_Version 0.6.10, Dec 2021.
1. Minor schema modifications in 'TaxonDetermination'
2. Changed repository location to 'iavs-org'

_Version 0.6.10, June 2021.
1. Update of schema veg-misc.xsd: simpleUserDefinedType has now a choice between attribute or methodID (suggested by Sebastian Schmidtlein).

_Version 0.6.9, November 2018.
1. Update documentation of 'addSiteObservations'

_Version 0.6.8, July 2018.
1. Specify predefined methods using strings only
2. Table with predefined methods
3. Update 'addSiteObservations'

_Version 0.6.7, July 2018.
1. Bug correction in 'addPlotGeometries' (reported by F. Jansen)
2. Redefinition of schema elements for individual organisms (mainly location)
3. VegX schema version changed to '2.0.1'

_Version 0.6.6, May 2018.
1. Cleaning for CRAN (check).

_Version 0.6.5, March 2018.
1. Bug correction readVegXML/writeVegXML 'taxon' to 'taxonName'.

_Version 0.6.4, February 2018.
1. New function 'addCommunityObservations()' added.
2. New predefined measurement method: basal area.
3. showElementTable() modified to display community observations.
4. Update function 'addTaxonBySiteData'.


